Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppression fire only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take this one alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tight formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me MECH never considered that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an open channel distress signal from an injured Decpeticon might be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bear that in mind next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha, next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decepticon radio chatter's all abuzz about the workover you gave poor Breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an ex-Con myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really should have disarrayed you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, an old acquaintance and her nasty little human destoried my ship and skinned my knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean to pay them back in kind, both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make it in and out of place as most Decepticons can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm still learning to navigate this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in it for MECH?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you came to collect that "Transformer", was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw in whatever is left of Arcee,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after I've broken her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Thanks for walking me home, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}You're a real gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}I don't want you reved up before bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Mom's a light sleeper, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}I don't think that she'd understand about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Understand what, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}You breaking curfew for the third time this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Or why your boss called about you missing another shifted work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Or maybe the email I received from your art-history teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}who's concerned you've been falling asleep in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, two words, mom, art and history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the rumors aren't true Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you're not racing that motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, wait... Where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small town, people talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I work in an emergency room, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen what can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, tell me you haven't fallen in with the bad crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no. My friends are the good crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let you have that bike because you convinced me you are mature enough to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you may need a gentle reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Message received, mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we had this talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's see if a few weeks without the distraction of your motorcycle will do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No but! You're grounded from everything but school, and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you want to take a bike to either,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious face, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see that motorcycle out of the garage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go wash up and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you while you're grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry Arcee. I'll visit you here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting on my fat tire for two weeks is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no... You saw mom's serious face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Arcee, I feel badly enough that I had to lie to her all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's gonna think that I'm blowing her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep breath Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom works late nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to be back in the garage before she gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... no promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, I hope you're not planning to eat take-out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took my break early so I could cook my grounded son a wholesome dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-organic tofu! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, eh, car beats ten-speed. I'll be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, pick up, pick up, pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee! You wouldn't be in the garage right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk about this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Mom's on her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't race back there right now, I will be grounded for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mom will make me sell you for parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee, can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, I need to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack! I can't believe you disobeyed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right where I left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get one of your crew to sneak it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you just walk it up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, mom. You really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fasten your seatbelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My motorcycle is a sentient robotic organism from a distant planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,part of a team stationed here on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting a secret war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I spent most of my time after school hanging with her crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the coolest thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this isn't even her actual form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really a giant robot, who can transform into a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK, Arcee, show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is... She's shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more hiding, no more lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, roll out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, em,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bad crowd you've been hanging out with is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,science fiction club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will continue this when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the support, "partner".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me, remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ship's black box sustained serious damage in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our software was able to reconstruct a few frames from the security thingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our facial recognition algorithm will send Jack's image across the web--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,another kind of web.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... the mother lode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Government database?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Social networking page.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything worth knowing about Jack Darby is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age sixteen, Jasper, Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... June Darby, a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm being too hard on Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only way he's gonna learn is if I stick to my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee, is mom home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just bridged from base to beat her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there's a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MECH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know where I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know things about your family that even you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, do you know where your mother is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Jack. We have no intention of hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, we'd like to reunite the two of you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need you and Arcee to follow the GPS coordinates programmed into this communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll lead you to the temporary facility I've set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not mention our communicator scrambles the signal and your brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any break in communication or attempt to reach the other Autobots,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Miss Darby... Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to feel responsible for the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to her because of my connection to all this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, MECH is only interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they get what they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll let your mom go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly reasuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for June?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hanging around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Airachnid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help them, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are humen like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let Airachnid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few human lives are a small price to pay for a miracle of science like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will have a private session later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still learning about human kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but one thing is clear to me, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people care deeply about family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the sweetest revenge I could possibly devise
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be to make you watch as I take your family apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hurt my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You remember how much I enjoy sport,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll give you the opportunity to save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stashed her close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can rescue her before the stroke of twelve,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let both of you go unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let her do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can let us go. We won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom? Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I know we promised the spider-bot that she would have first crack at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but something tells me she plans to turn our mutual crisscross...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... into a double-cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silas, we don't have the means of transporting it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to cut and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I get in this, this... stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, mom. I'm gonna get you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, the robots are real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beat your deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'fraid not, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The task wasn't for you to find your mother by mid-night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a seat, sit back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy the horror show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make haste, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't worry about making a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have all the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you get to choose, agonizing, or excruciating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, your mother wants to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave her "dangling".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster. Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have time to take one part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go straight for the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the outcome, the spoils will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Jack. If you won't decide,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's lady's choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, your motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can explain, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MECH lost Breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were the odds they can't hold on to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaaaaack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, June.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the creepy crawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can let us go. We won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known Con were involved, I would have called in Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might have been too much for mom to handle in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it's done. Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs Darby,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm special agent William Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time you knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past several months, Jack's been... interning for me at the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler, mom's not gonna buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess-- without a trace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she would be your...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motorcycle, guardian, Autobot, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Arcee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Arcee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time for that ride you once made me promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, meet my science fiction club.
